configset listname post_lifetime = [VALUE]
- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
Default Value : 60
Data Type     : integer
Category      : moderate
Password Notes: Visible only with password.
= = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = =

EXAMPLE:
configset listname post_lifetime = -1


$INCLUDE-config/post_lifetime

The "post" trigger in the triggers configuration setting determines how
often old statistics are erased.

Statistics will never be erased if this setting has a negative value.


